    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i was looking at my warfarin pills. ive been on 5mg for a while now and i honestly feel great. been eating super healthy and i dont feel like i need such a high dose anymore. is it okay if i just drop down to 2mg to keep it steady? i dont want to be on too much if i dont have to",
